    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Beastbound》</strong> 是一款融合了 Roguelike 和怪物驯养元素的游戏，灵感来源于基于卡牌的地牢探索游戏以及其他怪物驯养游戏中的玩家自制挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197940/extras/eddaafa75afe4ea99833055f423b86a6.webp?t=1756724775\" width=600 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每次冒险中，你都会遇到不同的怪物、物品和事件，每次都能带来独特的游戏体验。尝试不同的组合，扩展你的团队，并充分利用有限的资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197940/extras/b972d56b54b970f62e1ed8073f27417c.poster.avif?t=1756724775\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197940/extras/b972d56b54b970f62e1ed8073f27417c.webm?t=1756724775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197940/extras/b972d56b54b970f62e1ed8073f27417c.mp4?t=1756724775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197940/extras/13a7ad1e39299b00972861002eb7f04c.webp?t=1756724775\" width=600 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的怪物在每场战斗之间都会保留它们的生命值！谨慎行事，照顾好你的团队，因为你的每一个决定都可能影响怪物的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197940/extras/e1f717fa395c1e67778bef0c0b6460b1.webp?t=1756724775\" width=600 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从众多为支持各种玩法风格设计的物品和神器中进行选择，彻底改变你的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197940/extras/e32db2a9bf6343387459650dc94b36c5.webp?t=1756724775\" width=600 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对会根据你在战斗中的选择、地图上的行动，甚至是运气而变化和适应的首领！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>加入我们的 Discord 获取最新更新信息！</strong><br>我们不断添加新内容，尝试实验性的可选功能，并不断优化游戏。加入我们的 Discord，第一时间获取最新更新通知！</p>",
